starlark-go-bazel
Copyright 2026 Alberto Cavalcante

This project implements Bazel's Starlark dialect in Go. It is a clean-room
implementation that references Bazel's public API and documented behavior,
but does not copy code from Bazel.

This project uses the following dependencies:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
go.starlark.net - Starlark interpreter in Go
Copyright 2017 The Bazel Authors
License: BSD-3-Clause
https://github.com/google/starlark-go
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Bazel project, which defines the Starlark dialect this project implements:
https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel
Copyright 2014 The Bazel Authors
License: Apache-2.0

While this implementation references Bazel's API design and documented behavior
for compatibility, no Bazel source code has been copied into this project.
